Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will chase after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you go left, I'll go right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council President, they're running in the halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let them off this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say when I catch her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, you've always wanted to know, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Takasu Ryuuji too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love him! I've always loved him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought I should let you have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought to myself, "If Taiga, my best friend, needs him..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that was just my arrogance confusing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've underestimated you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that my happiness doesn't depend on anyone but me, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you. Your happiness doesn't depend on anyone but yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see what you're going to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I tripped while I was running...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:46.08,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz8\pos(630,186)\c&H20334D&}Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it stopped yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were crying for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought I would cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course... Normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this is sort of a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when I talked about what I can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's my willpower...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Willpower?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you my brother plays baseball, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to play baseball too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was better than him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't keep playing because I'm a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I plan to save money,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then get into a sports university and aim for the national softball league.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll shout out to the whole world:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This is the happiness I chose and achieved!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because I was obsessive about it, I decided to not to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's hard and painful, I've decided I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone sees me go through hardship and pain and cry, I guess it's a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that hairpin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the present you wanted to give to me on Christmas Eve, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I really didn't know at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a present from Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I decided to not take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to apologize for wearing it in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that hairpin right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in my room, but{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there's something else that I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that you like Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Takasu-kun, this is a giant goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run toward the thing that you can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ka-su, hey! Ta-ka-su, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ka-su!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an honest person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come to work even though you ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, about what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... uh{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Minorin's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh at me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... If I want to run away again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to hold on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our paycheck's pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You both lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so spoiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Takasu-kun, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for always taking care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, she'll be staying with{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'd stay with you, that man and that brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who doesn't get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you wouldn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you lied and broke that promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fainted because you pushed yourself too much for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm working in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're a family, we should help each other out{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to concentrate on your studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to find something you want to do and live a good life{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one who didn't concentrate on their studies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who couldn't do what they want and failed in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit forcing your failure's on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Taiga!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.14,0:07:38.14,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fs48\pos(1043.636364,523.5)}Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damned old man's business failed and he ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he told my real mom to take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she already has a new family,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's even pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her new husband is tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so their child will definitely have long legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pale in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... How can I fit in with a family like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were there, I'd only make everything awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same at the damn old man's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my presence, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had never been born, Yasuko would definitely have a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still young, so she could probably redo high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults are really selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They bring others trouble because of their own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might be the one who's troubling Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still a child, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, if I had never been born{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you pig-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're misunderstanding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Idiot! Idiot! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baldy! Baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you solve by doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say something naive like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly what you were saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you spend your life with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to be able to see you, Takasu Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... That's why you can't say things like "If only I had never been born"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, that sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really dwell on trivial things, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What blood type are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Taurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with horoscopes, but roast lamb is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be eighteen in two months!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run away from Yasuko and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run and run,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll sleep and wake up and then I'll run until it's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, we'll both be adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life will be yours until I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lov{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so unfair! Didn't I tell you to listen to what I have to say first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sneaky dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proposing should be left to guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, I made a promise with Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to show her what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then let's say it together...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lo{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lov{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is calling at such an important time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going, it's getting cold here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?! It'll be a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pick it up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu, what the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom and Aisaka's mom are searching everywhere for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just come to where I tell you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Kitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sneezed on my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two all wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we meeting at your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mothers haven't come here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My aunt isn't here today, so come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold if you stay in those clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a shower first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this and this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I'm troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga, your shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Yuusaku said he'll bring you a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I'm sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You love Taiga, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who forced me to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?! How could you?! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin! Minorin, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura, I'm sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.89,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga! Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Anyway, what are you guys planning to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...plan to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two more months, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you supporting them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away and then getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Ryuuji turns eighteen, we'll{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, where will you be living?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay in a business hotel or maybe even a manga cafe for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to live like that forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Well, after I come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagine search parties looking for you and everyone at school finding out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two might even get expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things I want just end up breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided to not desire anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my feelings were rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to break this "all the things I want just end up breaking" jinx.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my savings that I always hold onto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my life savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, Taiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think your actions are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be able to approve of them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this is what you want to do, I have no right to object to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay me back one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the key to my villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been there already, so you should know how to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some things to discuss with A-min.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why do I have to{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're friends again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, stupid chi-.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again, Minorin, stupid chi-.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to discuss with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your hand off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so weak that I can't even stand anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? You wanted to show me your crying face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying is a nosebleed of the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Taiga took Takasu-kun away from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I decided to never cry again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've understood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you trip while running down a hallway, you'll get a nosebleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you trip in life, you'll cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early for us to be talking about life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, for ten years, for twenty years, for sixty years,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,life will go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to run out once you've got your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Ya-chan{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Oh yeah! Remember to bring your hair dryer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to carry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring too much light clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be dead weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out right after you're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens, call me immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inko-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.12,Hand,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz350\pos(868,104)\c&H281F17&\fad(0, 300)}To: Ryuu-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to your grandparents' house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them this watch and they'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mirano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called at dawn saying she'll be taking a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after my birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll still be a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been showing it off since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it already; just how long do you plan to show it off for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until it expires.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the one who said that school isn't a place for trading chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trading. I'm just bringing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they catch a cold together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like a "fever."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight on! Fight on! Fight on! Fight on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oohashi! Fight on! Fight on! Fight on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:28.39,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to see them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless how strong of a will she has,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she broke down after being dumped by both Taiga and Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to have a snowball fight with{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Pure white sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's food for running away, I picked something more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, cigar chocolate, chicken wafers and{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made lunch too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you buy lunch from train stations when you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She only cares about her own reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she'll make a big fuss out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about Ya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only say it now because we're running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when Ya-chan said we're a family of three,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was truly overjoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what my "family" is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... When we're really becoming a family like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will Ya-chan cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be goodbye forever! It's not that I don't want to run away with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's great, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:21.92,Hand,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,234)\c&H757468&}Takasu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! D-D-D-D-D-D-D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you; I am your grandchild, Takasu Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, she's my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not escaping, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:22:05.03,Preview Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(323.636364,204)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:22:05.03,Preview Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs82.5\pos(923.636364,552)}Toradora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji showed me his method of dealing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh at me. Don't get mad at me.
